  "original_title": "Tyeab Akbarally joins Sunshine Holdings Board",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Tyeab Akbarally joins Sunshine Holdings Board",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tyeab Akbarally has been appointed as a Non-Independent Non-Executive Director on the Board of Sunshine Holdings PLC.",
        "Akbarally has been a Director of Akbar Brothers Group of Companies since 1979, and presently holds the position of the Managing Director and is actively engaged in the Tea and Commodity Export Trade. He was a former Chairman of The Colombo Tea Traders Association, and Spices and Allied Products Producers\u2019 and Traders\u2019 Association. He was also a Director of Amana Bank and the Chairman of Amana Takaful PLC and is on the Boards of several other companies",
        "Akbar Brothers holds 49.2 million shares or 10% stake in Sunshine Holdings.",
        "With the latest appointment, the Board of Directors of Sunshine Holdings comprises Chairman Amal Cabraal, Group Managing Director V. Govindasamy, S. Ratwatte, H.D. Abeywickrama, A.D.B. Talwatte, S. Shishoo, G. Sathasivam, S.G. Sathasivam, S. Jain, W.Y.R. Fernando, S. Renganathan and T. Akbarally."
      ],
